overview: A conversation between a pisces and a capricorn about stifling isolation and nurturing solitude.  Nicky Chue is a queer BPOC filmmaker from Berlin who spends a lot of their time sitting in nature and identifying bees.  Florence Low  is a queer British Armenian artist, graphic designer, photographer, drag king and dreamy Pisces. They are currently obsessed with Kate Bush, cats, queer space in London, astrology and attachment styles.
title: woodland
